0.005   2019-01-28  Released-By: PERLANCAR

	- Add option --dereference-files (-D), like in du.


0.004   2019-01-27  Released-By: PERLANCAR

	- bin-files-into-dvds: [ux] Use a more conservative DVD size default
          (4494MB -> 4470MB) so they fit more.


0.003   2019-01-17  Released-By: PERLANCAR

	- Add utility: count-number-of-dvs-required.

	- Add option --num-bins (-n) to return just the number of bins/dvds
	  required.

	- [ux] Rename --bin-size to --dvd-size for bin-files-into-dvds.

	- [doc] Add more keywords.


0.002   2019-01-16  Released-By: PERLANCAR

	- bin-files-into-dvds: allow overriding --bin-size (-s) which
	  defaults to 4493M.


0.001   2019-01-16  Released-By: PERLANCAR

        - First release.
